{"tid":1754472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly仲有手足未走","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T09:05:40.000Z","uid":183595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a76f8a45e73b64b7407bcd821378b87c5c7dd6","tid":1754472,"uid":183595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y2BLfGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy2BLfGU.jpg&h=0d64e5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RBCuHnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRBCuHnM.png&h=504bc6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日區選贏左，係近呢幾個月最令人振奮既事，我同大家一樣都好開心！<br />\n<br />\n但希望大家都唔好忘記仲有手足喺Poly入面受緊苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地好需要我地支持架，大家可唔可以一齊出黎聲援下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能唔係唱歌但希望大家都可以做少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n贏左區選只係我地既第一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要一齊繼續贏落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"620c351f33309cd59cf8ff68fb77dbd74fb6fcc8","tid":1754472,"uid":186152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n屌你老母 藍田撚唔認J19個投票結果呀 造票造到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1754379/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1754379/page/1</a><br />\n【冇人知】八鄉北點票失誤 鄉事派16票之差勝選 落選人擬提選舉呈請<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754387</a><br />\n[元朗屏山北][搞大佢]區選仲未完仲可以再爭取!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754167</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFdd8SA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/th